<li><a href="http://stairwayblues.tumblr.com/">Stairwayblues</a> is an artist with a colorful style and, well, since we have a tale about <a href="/scp-2030">2030</a> this month, why not link you a wonderful picture of it? Here's <a href="http://stairwayblues.tumblr.com/post/135918581236/happy-holidays-folks-d">SCP-2030</a> in all of its suave, charming glory. Laugh is indeed fun, and also colorful to boot!</li>
