<h4 id="toc20"><span>Top-Rated Articles of 2015</span></h4>
<p>2015 has been a massive year, hasn't it? Lots of cool skips and tales have come and showed their staying power. So what are the top-rated ones of the year? Here are the Top 10 for SCPs and tales! (Well, in both cases, more than that.)</p>
